---
title: Dill-Garlic Chicken with Creamy Veggie Orzo
description: Subtle and sweet dill flavours reign supreme in this recipe. Dill-Garlic Spice Blend coats the chicken breast before it is seared and roasted and then served atop luxurious green orzo laced with zucchini and tender spinach.
